"'''The Lost Lightsaber'''" is a [[Star Wars comic books|comic]] from ''[[Star Wars Tales 19]]'' and collected in ''[[Star Wars Tales Volume 5]]''.

==Plot summary==
The young [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]] [[Ben Skywalker]] recovers his [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|grandfather's]] [[Anakin Skywalker's second lightsaber/Legends|lightsaber]] from a group of [[Dark Jedi/Legends|Dark Jedi]] who are attempting to fuse [[Dark side of the Force/Legends|dark side]] energies into it.

